unit1 $HOME/challenge/unit1に移動してみよう
```
cd unit1
ls
cat answer1.txt
```

unit2 $HOME/challenge/unit2でanswer2.txtを作成してみよう
```
cd unit2
touch answer2.txt
cat answer2.txt
```

unit3 $HOME/challenge/unit3からcd jp/hogera/../fuga/../../en/foo/barを実行した後カレントディレクトリを確認して
```
cd unit3
cd jp/hogera/../fuga/../../en/foo/bar
pwd
cat answer3.txt
```

unit4 $HOME/challenge/unit4でanswer4.txt.tmpをanswer4.txtに名前を変更しよう
```
cd unit4
mv answer4.txt.tmp answer4.txt
cat answer4.txt
```

unit5 $HOME/challenge/unit5でanswerディレクトリを作ってanswer1.txt, answer2.txt, answer3.txt, answer4.txtをanswerにコピーしてanswer5.txtを作成
```
cd unit5
mkdir answer
cd answer
cp ../../unit1/answer1.txt ./
cp ../../unit2/answer2.txt ./
cp ../../unit3/en/foo/bar/answer3.txt ./
cp ../../unit4/answer4.txt ./
touch answer5.txt
cat answer5.txt
```

unit6 $HOME/challenge/unit6でテキストエディタを使ってdate.txtに今日の日付をyyyy/mm/dd形式で書いてみよう
```
cd unit6
vim date.txt
2023/08/05
:wq
cat answer6.txt
```

unit7 $HOME/challenge/unit7のcolors.txtからanswer7.txtのパスを探そう
```
cd unit7
less colors.txt
/unit
q
cd ../unit3/jp/fuga/fugafuga
cat answer7.txt
```
unit8 answer8.txtを探して
```
cd unit8
find -name answer8.txt
cd 2023/8/5
cat answer8.txt
```
